<em>Custom Labels<\/em> area.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large screen-capture\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"540\" src=\"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/add-label-1024x540.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-3598\" srcset=\"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/add-label-1024x540.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/add-label-300x158.jpg 300w, https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/add-label-768x405.jpg 768w, https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/add-label-1536x810.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/add-label-150x79.jpg 150w, https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/11\/add-label.jpg 1585w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>In general product label reflect on the status of product using stock quantity and arrival time. WooCommerce plugin support 4 statuses including Feature, New, Sale and Out of Stock. Based on wooCommerce plugin, you can add custom label to product. It helps users to get more information about product. Then, head to Dashboard &gt; Products [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[8],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1773"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpr